  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the study is to know if the reconstruction of the lower limb mechanical axis and
      the patient knee function is improved after Total Knee Arthroplasty (TKA) using patient
      specific instruments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
